<HEAD>Sandinistas Say Contras Attack; Farmers Praise Calm</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By BRYNA BRENNAN</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>LAS COLINAS, Nicaragua (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
